name: Warmup_Div04_Sub04
queryText:
SELECT DISTINCT
GmailD4S4.CPF,
GmailD4S4.NOME,
GmailD4S4.EMAIL,
GmailD4S4.EMAIL_VALIDO,
CASE

  WHEN CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD4S4.NOME) = 0 THEN GmailD4S4.NOME

  ELSE SUBSTRING( GmailD4S4.NOME , 1, CHARINDEX(' ', GmailD4S4.NOME) )

END AS PNOME
FROM Gmail_DIV04_SUB04 GmailD4S4
UNION
